{"about_the_game":"<strong>Dark Hope is a puzzle adventure game set in a steampunk world where electricity started and ended its existence with the light bulb.</strong><br><br><i>Strange rifts of light span the shadowed hallways. <br><br>Something lurks in the dark.<br><br>Your only hope of freedom is to find the truth about this strange abandoned facility.<br><br>You wake up in a hallway: No one is around. Where the exit once was is now darkness, and smoke fills the air...<br><br>Where are you? <br><br>...Where did everyone go?</i><br><br>The vast majority of the puzzles are environmental mechanical puzzles and discovering clues as to the nature of this strange facility.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A first-person adventure full of environmental mechanical puzzles.<br></li><li>Discover clues as you solve puzzles to uncover the true nature of this strange facility.<br></li><li>Books! Tons and tons of books filled with lab notes, plans, and clues.<br></li><li>Buttons to push and valves to turn- In Dark Hope, the environment is the puzzle.<br></li><li>A challenging, atmospheric puzzle-adventure for those who don\u2019t want to be spoon-fed.<br></li><li>Eerie and haunting atmosphere- What happened here? What will happen if you don\u2019t figure that out?<br></li><li>Warning: Bring your own notebook and pen!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Access The BioLab","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/620350/4f749eca9c724687d109efc87032357f1815ae78.jpg"},{"name":"Access The Energy Lab","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/620350/d5120c9a8b49fc325a036d85f7911f2f48251ead.jpg"},{"name":"Access the Mechanical Lab","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/620350/70c87cb71d30f7680c8cf5a15c4675509effe838.jpg"},{"name":"Access portal lab","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/620350/